Aggregating data¶

Maksudnya grouping data dulu lalu di average karena dalam sehari bisa banyak reviews sehingga lebih memudahkan proses¶

In [ ]:
data['Day'] = data['Timestamp'].dt.date # .dt.month / dt."dan lain lain" method tentang date time
# data.head()
day_average = data.groupby(['Day']).mean() # Aggregasi based on mean per day
day_average.head()

# "Day" merupakan index jadi untuk akses harus:

What day are people the happiest on?¶

In [ ]:
data['Weekday'] = data['Timestamp'].dt.strftime("%A") # %A is for weekday
data["Daynumber"] = data["Timestamp"].dt.strftime("%w") # %w urutan angka harinya
weekday_average = data.groupby(['Weekday', 'Daynumber']).mean()
weekday_average = weekday_average.sort_values('Daynumber') # Untuk sorting
weekday_average
